{"id": 2207, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得哪些逞“男子气概”的做法是不必要的？", "description": "许多男孩被困在一种“你不能表现出脆弱，否则等于被阉割”的男子气概陷阱里，但逞强就算男子汉？", "record_count": 4695, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201803042329597amj2U9CRwgVfk6e.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-03-05T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 268544, "content": "都很有必要", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 684635}, {"id": 268546, "content": "所以可以回答多次咯？", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1277598}, {"id": 268547, "content": "明明没钱 但是碍面子 又装大方 抢着给钱 还不让别人还 别人还比他有钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1267003}, {"id": 268548, "content": "感情深，一口闷。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1212756}, {"id": 270087, "content": "大男子主义，女的就该听男的的，这种我一个男的看了都恶心", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1284092}, {"id": 268553, "content": "应酬谈生意永远不能不喝酒", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1278221}, {"id": 268557, "content": "抢着买单", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1278175}, {"id": 269588, "content": "吃饭一定要男的付钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1281739}, {"id": 268565, "content": "宽容女性对男性的物化", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1053401}, {"id": 269589, "content": "特别爱不懂装懂 那个什么啊 我知道", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1282505}, {"id": 274198, "content": "吹牛逼，假装自己知识渊博，人缘广", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1303811}, {"id": 268569, "content": "学到点皮毛就在女生面前表现像个行家", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1277830}, {"id": 270366, "content": "硬上！对双关！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1284705}, {"id": 271135, "content": "吹?，喝酒，抽烟，满口脏话，所谓的社会人。拿着父母的钱去装。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1289433}, {"id": 269603, "content": "骂脏话", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1251032}, {"id": 269092, "content": "我", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1234473}, {"id": 268846, "content": "死要面子", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 998717}, {"id": 270388, "content": "对女生太宠，最后受苦的是自己。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 921908}, {"id": 269365, "content": "在文科班，与不讨人喜欢的老师抬杠", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1218387}, {"id": 269368, "content": "看完这上面说的，有好几条，感觉都不是男人一开始就喜欢这样做的，比如里面说的难受不说出来，不去沟通通过喝酒来发泄，或者是下班在车里躲着，我认为没有一个男人一开始就喜欢这样做，大家觉得呢？这是个人见解，不喜勿喷啊。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1007899}, {"id": 271160, "content": "他说我觉得应该怎么样……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1289784}, {"id": 269113, "content": "大度 幽默 让着女人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1098965}, {"id": 268604, "content": "你觉得女生哪些“故作聪明”的做法是没有必要的？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1278281}, {"id": 268860, "content": "不穿秋衣秋裤", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1279345}, {"id": 269628, "content": "什么都不会说，就算再难受的默默憋到心里，假装坚强挺傻的，其实我还可以给个抱抱", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1282855}, {"id": 273725, "content": "要面子，即使打肿脸充胖子也死要面子，其实完全没必要。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1300535}, {"id": 268606, "content": "吹牛逼，讲黄段子，力气大。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 746493}, {"id": 268607, "content": "男儿膝下有黄金", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1278409}, {"id": 269639, "content": "抽烟，喝酒，大牌", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1282925}, {"id": 269390, "content": "抽烟，喝酒，吹牛，拍马。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1092406}, {"id": 268629, "content": "这么点酒量，还是男人吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1278461}, {"id": 268885, "content": "酒量。酒量是基因决定的，锻炼，只是让自己的身体，习惯受到伤害。这真的很可怜", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1272823}, {"id": 268376, "content": "声称自己“（枪击案里）没有枪我也会冲上去！”", "image": null, "praise_count": 266, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 268377, "content": "感冒了拒绝吃药，表示这点小病扛扛就过去了", "image": null, "praise_count": 184, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 268378, "content": "跟人闹矛盾了“就是硬气！就是干！”", "image": null, "praise_count": 354, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 268891, "content": "恋爱男生要主动", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1279058}, {"id": 268639, "content": "如果你们说的这些行为都是不必要的，那么男人和女人又有什么区别？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1169037}, {"id": 268396, "content": "一定要抽烟、喝酒、一定要会吹牛逼。", "image": null, "praise_count": 850, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1204231}, {"id": 268397, "content": "斜着脑袋自拍", "image": null, "praise_count": 42, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1125313}, {"id": 268398, "content": "开黄腔", "image": null, "praise_count": 559, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1266340}, {"id": 268654, "content": "在看“你觉得哪些逞“男子气概”的做法是不必要的？”的同时审视自己还“欠缺”哪些", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 81517}, {"id": 268399, "content": "怎么能让女生出钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 404, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1264212}, {"id": 268400, "content": "雷厉风行，不必听别人的建议和意见", "image": null, "praise_count": 70, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1141400}, {"id": 268401, "content": "一定能搞事情，一定骚得起来", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1259239}, {"id": 269425, "content": "直男癌", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1281397}, {"id": 268402, "content": "抽烟喝酒", "image": null, "praise_count": 53, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1276522}, {"id": 268403, "content": "轮到你们女人说话了吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 554, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 524906}, {"id": 268404, "content": "难受不能说出来 情绪都憋在心里 通过喝酒而不是沟通发泄", "image": null, "praise_count": 242, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1216775}, {"id": 268405, "content": "各位的评论我都想点赞", "image": null, "praise_count": 39, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 781199}, {"id": 268406, "content": "男人怎么能说不行", "image": null, "praise_count": 141, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1277352}]}